Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.51,0:00:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多之星即將開幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.75,0:00:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家觀看時請注意保持室內光明 請儘量遠離電視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.06,0:00:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.22,0:00:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有沒有過“已經不行了”的感覺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.97,0:00:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了極限的極限 怎麼努力也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.89,0:00:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為有等待著自己的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.97,0:00:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有鼓勵自己、嚴格要求自己的、互相信任的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.51,0:00:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的不是我一個人！個人！個人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.70,0:02:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去河邊洗衣服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.73,0:02:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特？茱莉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.76,0:02:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來了啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.77,0:02:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.47,0:02:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.99,0:02:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.04,0:02:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 和由利意見不合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.76,0:02:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說可能被解雇了的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.68,0:02:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空呢 還在努力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.94,0:02:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本不是什麼努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超極寒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確切點說是在拼命哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我早就沒命了的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.12,0:02:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那丫頭還真行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對她有點另眼相看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.65,0:02:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在做什麼樣的訓練呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.72,0:03:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到夢幻的超絕技完成之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們每天都會舉辦一個相關節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望各位觀眾務必光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團的節目越來越精彩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.12,0:03:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過聽說即使夢幻的超絕技失敗的話也不會退票？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說都是前任老闆的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.14,0:03:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於FREEDOMRIZE的突然倒戈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.34,0:03:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從內心感到悲痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.70,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次的退款對於我們經營方也是個損失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.29,0:03:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這次是明確了大家都能夠接受之後才會售票的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.47,0:03:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 人們有沒有什麼不滿的情緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.12,0:03:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有傳聞說上次挑戰的是您的父親...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.89,0:03:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過家父在練習中因為事故不幸亡故了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.93,0:03:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 竟然是那麼難的技巧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.00,0:04:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就我個人來說這次無論如何要成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.14,0:04:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預定屆時將由本台進行現場直播
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.63,0:04:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個夢幻的超絕技怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是不可能完成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.30,0:04:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,99%公演會取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.27,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用夢幻的超絕技的宣傳效果來挽回了觀眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相關周邊產品的銷售也非常順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是多虧了夢幻的超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.12,0:04:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取消之後我會宣佈我和蕾拉將再次挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣一來宣傳的效果將……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出終止，卡萊多劇團也解散吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.25,0:04:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也將出售卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這麼交給你管 所受的損失就大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.08,0:04:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大股東雅格尼斯大叔都這麼說一定不會錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.58,0:04:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.97,0:05:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美亞 阿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.83,0:05:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.41,0:05:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬納森和大家還好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.74,0:05:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快別說話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.82,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.12,0:05:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.69,0:05:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.94,0:05:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分吧 這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.97,0:05:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不努力的話會追不上蕾拉小姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.78,0:05:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.61,0:05:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是亂來，是我的特訓……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.65,0:05:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.49,0:05:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健，必須讓空休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.58,0:05:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她回宿舍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.19,0:05:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說，怎麼可以弄得渾身是傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.60,0:06:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健也真是的，我還以為你會好好保護空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！完了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼在睡覺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.80,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去練習的話，會追不上蕾拉小姐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.49,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.18,0:06:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.38,0:06:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不多休息會是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不休息的話會累壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你練習的太過火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.37,0:06:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 不過我已經沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.90,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐已經開始更加困難的練習了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.13,0:06:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.19,0:06:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐也在進行著這樣傷痕累累的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.99,0:06:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的超絕技的難度看來比我們想像中的還要高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.59,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不說比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.95,0:07:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.29,0:07:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.34,0:07:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許這只是偶然成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須能連續十次才能算成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.71,0:07:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.05,0:07:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.98,0:07:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經漸漸地開始瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻的超絕技到底是什麼樣的絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真能完成真是太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.25,0:07:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以現在我和空的搭檔能完成嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐，你已經吃完了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.51,0:07:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，今天好像沒什麼食欲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.17,0:08:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始我在自己房間裏吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.51,0:08:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 連續十次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續下麵的練習了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想揮灑身體中更多激情的汗水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.96,0:08:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 無論發生什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.54,0:08:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要和你完成夢幻的超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.40,0:08:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.64,0:08:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是保持姿勢就這麼難了 她竟然能彈那麼高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.72,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要磨蹭到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.75,0:08:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.42,0:09:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐怎麼好像有點煩躁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.02,0:09:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 連吃飯都只願意一個人吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是夏洛特做的飯太難吃的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說 真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.29,0:09:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我覺得挺不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.47,0:09:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 啊~太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.99,0:09:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐很煩躁是因為我的實力還不夠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.83,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我真的能成為蕾拉小姐的搭檔嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.63,0:09:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練了一個星期 雖然已經有了安定感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總覺得力量跟不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是去幫夏洛特她們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.08,0:10:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.38,0:10:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐，為什麼什麼都不對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.01,0:10:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把勁啊 振作點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.11,0:10:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣下去沒有資格做我的搭檔什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.81,0:10:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說些什麼 無論什麼都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了，蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.71,0:10:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.36,0:10:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼要說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.55,0:11:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅格尼斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.63,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裏有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊? 到這裏來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.97,0:11:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼可憐的表情啊 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.52,0:11:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有半點鬥爭心 沒志氣的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.96,0:11:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點兒也不能讓人覺得你能夠表演那個夢幻超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛才練習結束 有些累...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那幫傢伙料中了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.65,0:11:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幫傢伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些對卡萊多劇團袖手不管的小傢伙們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.99,0:12:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們誰都不認為夢幻超絕技會成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.41,0:12:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這個期間的活動成功就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.92,0:12:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.59,0:12:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那天的公演取消 去除賠償的還綽綽有餘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是客人們...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.80,0:12:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的有絕對不辜負觀眾的期待的自信嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.63,0:12:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的有和蕾拉一起完成的自信嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有自信說“我就是蕾拉的搭檔”嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.01,0:12:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把勁啊 振作點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.75,0:12:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣下去沒有資格做我的搭檔什麼的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.83,0:12:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請說些什麼 無論什麼都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了，蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼要說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.33,0:13:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.07,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼特地來說這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.57,0:13:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對著拼命要把受傷的心重新振作的空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.57,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 去房裏休息一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.88,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我杯咖啡，少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫健•羅賓斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.54,0:13:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.50,0:13:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不出我一定作給你看什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.01,0:14:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心裏只想著蕾拉小姐能承認我這個搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.82,0:14:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這個地步才發現根本是我的實力不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.32,0:14:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才想著要逃避 真是無法原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 你已經很努力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.36,0:14:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我認為如果累了退出也是好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐也一定能理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.15,0:14:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前蕾拉小姐這麼跟我說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.17,0:14:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半吊子的覺悟只是會給人添麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.48,0:14:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我退出是為了蕾拉的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您大老遠的來一趟實在是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不過說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然覺得空是個能成大器的的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.16,0:14:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒想到她會去挑戰夢幻超絕技啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.14,0:14:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從亞倫•布拉斯開始嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.71,0:15:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在意那件事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔的念頭一直沒有辦法消退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.84,0:15:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他實在是個責任心強的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.19,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個挑戰真是太亂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.35,0:15:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團以前因挑戰夢幻超絕技\N而身亡的人是亞倫•布拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時團的超級明星—也就是由利的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也向喬確認過了 不會有錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.40,0:15:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多的人們從由利那裏聽說了這件事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.77,0:15:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒人相信會成功也是正常的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太在意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.06,0:15:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待著你們的絕技能夠平安完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.62,0:15:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由利和大家一樣，都不相信我會完成夢幻超絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.49,0:15:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就要看空怎麼應對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.63,0:16:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她能不能從那個穀底裏爬上來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.82,0:16:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果做不到這點，她是不可能完成夢幻的超絕技的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.62,0:16:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的，故意製造出這個穀底的正是你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.13,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們一直對空有所期待吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.47,0:16:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了讓我們體驗一下那個穀底你才撤資的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是原因之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.26,0:16:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想和那幫傢伙聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我送去給蕾拉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.35,0:16:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.70,0:16:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空說今天不吃晚飯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要靜一靜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.04,0:16:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.07,0:16:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.41,0:17:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…蕾拉小姐雖然不讓我說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.56,0:17:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐，我有話想和你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.43,0:17:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.96,0:17:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐現在不在房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去長跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長跑 在這種時間？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.39,0:17:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在減肥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,減肥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.97,0:17:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可能是兩個人的體重差越大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻超絕技的成功率就越低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.82,0:17:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得蕾拉小姐她已經知道夢幻超絕技是什麼樣的技巧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多快回來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.69,0:18:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉到這裏後一直是在自己的房間裏吃飯的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實際上根本沒吃什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.18,0:18:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏洛特說的 雖說蕾拉小姐叫她保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.98,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我害的，讓蕾拉小姐做這樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為搭檔是相等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.52,0:18:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就象你一直努力做好蕾拉小姐的好搭檔一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐也在努力的成為你的好搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.70,0:18:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直仰慕的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.56,0:18:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確，你有著我所沒有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.09,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始是我和你的真正的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.59,0:18:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的時候，和父母一起去看過卡萊多的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.08,0:19:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次表演象夢幻一樣的精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.58,0:19:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我沒有追尋到自己的未來之前\N我絕不會表演自己的最後一場演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.33,0:19:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我有著為了同一目的而奮鬥的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.80,0:19:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.36,0:19:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你們二個是最好的搭檔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.78,0:19:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.05,0:19:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.64,0:19:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.51,0:19:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我竟然想逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.40,0:19:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特訓又累又痛苦\N所以覺得自己沒有成為蕾拉的搭檔的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想著一個人逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.20,0:19:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不會再迷惘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.74,0:19:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會更加地更加地努力 趕上你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定讓夢幻超絕技成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.98,0:20:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是為了這個才來這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.90,0:20:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.38,0:20:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會多吃東西來增加肌肉的 所以不要再這樣減肥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.69,0:20:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.46,0:20:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈 真的振作起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.88,0:20:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒白白來一趟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.92,0:20:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從穀底爬上來的人很強的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才特地...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.99,0:20:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變聰明了嘛  那麼酒就拜託你了 少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.57,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫健•羅賓斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.95,0:20:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就讓我們作為搭檔互不隱瞞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.76,0:20:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.70,0:20:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.04,0:21:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能把挑戰特技的資格給她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.71,0:21:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運似乎將給予你們更加殘酷的試煉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.99,0:21:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠跨越這個障礙的話 時機就成熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.06,0:21:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這實在是過於殘酷的試煉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.55,0:21:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“女帝的逆位”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.70,0:21:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.99,0:21:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才肩膀不是撞到了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.12,0:21:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了平衡稍微擦到一下而已  不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.29,0:21:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還是去一下醫院比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.03,0:21:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那個時間了，好了 繼續吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.16,0:21:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.42,0:21:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 好像沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.04,0:22:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 由於減肥意識有些不清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.83,0:22:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀還能堅持一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.59,0:22:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 再堅持一下 再堅持一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.03,0:22:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣，在決戰前日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.20,0:22:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蕾拉小姐的傷超過了相信令人感到絕望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.85,0:22:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管這些 到底為什麼你要作到這一步
